ript(agent, prev_script, results) -> str`\n  - Send failed script and results to agent, return corrected script\n  - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n  - Verification: `grep \"_repair_script\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n\n- [ ] **T7.3**: Define `_execute_once_in_runner` function\n  - Purpose: Execute script in sandbox\n  - Signature: `def _execute_once_in_runner(runner, pcap_path, script) -> Dict[str, Any]`\n  - Write script to sandbox, execute, return results\n  - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n  - Verification: `grep \"_execute_once_in_runner\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n\n- [ ] **T7.4**: Define `_analyze_with_retries` function\n  - Purpose: Orchestrate analysis with retry loop\n  - Signature: `def _analyze_with_retries(runner, pcap_path, max_retries=MAX_RETRIES) -> Dict[str, Any]`\n  - Plan script, execute, repair on failure, retry up to max_retries\n  - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n  - Verification: `grep \"_analyze_with_retries\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n\n- [ ] **T7.5**: Define `_report` function\n  - Purpose: Generate report via reporter agent\n  - Signature: `def _report(agent, results) -> str`\n  - Synthesize execution outputs into human-readable report\n  - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n  - Verification: `grep \"_report\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n\n### Phase 8: Response Model (ST-8)\n\n- [ ] **T8.1**: Define `AnalyzeResponse` Pydantic model\n  - Purpose: API response schema\n  - Fields: `script: str`, `results: List[Dict[str, Any]]`, `report: str`\n  - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n  - Verification: `grep \"class AnalyzeResponse\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n\n### Phase 9: FastAPI Application (ST-9)\n\n- [ ] **T9.1**: Create FastAPI app instance\n  - Purpose: Application entry point\n  - Code: `app = FastAPI(title=\"PCAP Analyzer\")`\n  - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n  - Verificat